Author: sweatyandsweet
Text: I sat an exam the other day and my stomach was rumbling the entire time. Like, really loudly. I might have to have breakfast next time so I don't distract everyone in the room. It was so embarrassing.

Author: evaa98
Text: I have exams too and it sucks. Because I feel like I have to eat to be able to learn and get good grades. But I am gaining weight, losing control and don't even enjoy the food
